{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Thank you so much everyone from TED, and Chris and Amy in particular."},{"time":5000,"text":"I cannot believe I'm here."},{"time":7000,"text":"I have not slept in weeks."},{"time":9000,"text":"Neil and I were sitting there comparing how little we've slept"},{"time":12000,"text":"in anticipation for this. I've never been so nervous --"},{"time":15000,"text":"and I do this when I'm nervous, I just realized. (Laughter)"},{"time":19000,"text":"So, I'm going to talk about sort of what we did at this organization"},{"time":23000,"text":"called 826 Valencia, and then I'm going to talk"},{"time":25000,"text":"about how we all might join in and do similar things."}]},{"cues":[{"time":28000,"text":"Back in about 2000, I was living in Brooklyn,"},{"time":32000,"text":"I was trying to finish my first book,"},{"time":35000,"text":"I was wandering around dazed every day"},{"time":37000,"text":"because I wrote from 12 a.m. to 5 a.m."},{"time":39000,"text":"So I would walk around in a daze during the day."},{"time":42000,"text":"I had no mental acuity to speak of during the day, but I had flexible hours."},{"time":50000,"text":"In the Brooklyn neighborhood that I lived in, Park Slope,"},{"time":53000,"text":"there are a lot of writers --"},{"time":55000,"text":"it's like a very high per capita ratio"},{"time":57000,"text":"of writers to normal people."},{"time":59000,"text":"Meanwhile, I had grown up around a lot of teachers."},{"time":64000,"text":"My mom was a teacher, my sister became a teacher"},{"time":66000,"text":"and after college so many of my friends went into teaching."},{"time":70000,"text":"And so I was always hearing them talk about their lives"},{"time":73000,"text":"and how inspiring they were,"},{"time":75000,"text":"and they were really sort of the most hard-working"},{"time":77000,"text":"and constantly inspiring people I knew."}]},{"cues":[{"time":79000,"text":"But I knew so many of the things they were up against,"},{"time":82000,"text":"so many of the struggles they were dealing with."},{"time":85000,"text":"And one of them was that so many of my friends"},{"time":88000,"text":"that were teaching in city schools were having trouble"},{"time":91000,"text":"with their students keeping up at grade level,"},{"time":94000,"text":"in their reading and writing in particular."},{"time":97000,"text":"Now, so many of these students had come from households"},{"time":99000,"text":"where English isn't spoken in the home,"},{"time":101000,"text":"where a lot of them have different special needs,"},{"time":105000,"text":"learning disabilities. And of course they're working in schools"},{"time":109000,"text":"which sometimes and very often are under-funded."},{"time":112000,"text":"And so they would talk to me about this and say,"},{"time":114000,"text":"\"You know, what we really need is just more people,"},{"time":116000,"text":"more bodies, more one-on-one attention,"},{"time":119000,"text":"more hours, more expertise from people"},{"time":122000,"text":"that have skills in English and can work with these students one-on-one.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":127000,"text":"Now, I would say, \"Well, why don't you just work with them one-on-one?\""},{"time":130000,"text":"And they would say, \"Well, we have five classes of 30 to 40 students each."},{"time":134000,"text":"This can lead up to 150, 180, 200 students a day."},{"time":138000,"text":"How can we possibly give each student"},{"time":141000,"text":"even one hour a week of one-on-one attention?\""},{"time":145000,"text":"You'd have to greatly multiply the workweek and clone the teachers."},{"time":149000,"text":"And so we started talking about this."},{"time":152000,"text":"And at the same time,"},{"time":154000,"text":"I thought about this massive group of people I knew:"},{"time":156000,"text":"writers, editors, journalists, graduate students,"},{"time":160000,"text":"assistant professors, you name it."},{"time":162000,"text":"All these people that had sort of flexible daily hours"},{"time":165000,"text":"and an interest in the English word --"},{"time":167000,"text":"I hope to have an interest in the English language,"},{"time":172000,"text":"but I'm not speaking it well right now. (Laughter)"},{"time":175000,"text":"I'm trying. That clock has got me."},{"time":179000,"text":"But everyone that I knew had an interest in the primacy of the written word"},{"time":184000,"text":"in terms of nurturing a democracy, nurturing an enlightened life."},{"time":188000,"text":"And so they had, you know, their time"},{"time":191000,"text":"and their interest, but at the same time"},{"time":194000,"text":"there wasn't a conduit that I knew of in my community"},{"time":198000,"text":"to bring these two communities together."}]},{"cues":[{"time":200000,"text":"So when I moved back to San Francisco, we rented this building."},{"time":204000,"text":"And the idea was to put McSweeney's --"},{"time":208000,"text":"McSweeney's Quarterly, that we published twice or three times a year,"},{"time":210000,"text":"and a few other magazines --"},{"time":212000,"text":"we were going to move it into an office for the first time."},{"time":215000,"text":"It used to be in my kitchen in Brooklyn."},{"time":217000,"text":"We were going to move it into an office,"},{"time":219000,"text":"and we were going to actually share space with a tutoring center."},{"time":222000,"text":"So we thought, \"We'll have all these writers and editors and everybody --"},{"time":225000,"text":"sort of a writing community -- coming into the office every day anyway,"},{"time":228000,"text":"why don't we just open up"},{"time":230000,"text":"the front of the building for students to come in there after school,"},{"time":232000,"text":"get extra help on their written homework,"},{"time":234000,"text":"so you have basically no border between these two communities?\""},{"time":238000,"text":"So the idea was that we would be"},{"time":242000,"text":"working on whatever we're working on,"},{"time":244000,"text":"at 2:30 p.m. the students flow in and you put down what you're doing,"},{"time":246000,"text":"or you trade, or you work a little bit later or whatever it is."},{"time":249000,"text":"You give those hours in the afternoon"},{"time":251000,"text":"to the students in the neighborhood."}]},{"cues":[{"time":253000,"text":"So, we had this place, we rented it,"},{"time":255000,"text":"the landlord was all for it. We did this mural,"},{"time":257000,"text":"that's a Chris Ware mural, that basically explains the entire history"},{"time":261000,"text":"of the printed word, in mural form -- it takes a long time"},{"time":263000,"text":"to digest and you have to stand in the middle of the road."},{"time":267000,"text":"So we rented this space."},{"time":269000,"text":"And everything was great except the landlord said,"},{"time":272000,"text":"\"Well, the space is zoned for retail; you have to come up with something."},{"time":274000,"text":"You've gotta sell something."},{"time":276000,"text":"You can't just have a tutoring center.\""},{"time":278000,"text":"So we thought, \"Ha ha! Really!\""},{"time":280000,"text":"And we couldn't think of anything necessarily to sell,"},{"time":283000,"text":"but we did all the necessary research."},{"time":285000,"text":"It used to be a weight room, so there were rubber floors below,"},{"time":288000,"text":"acoustic tile ceilings and fluorescent lights."},{"time":291000,"text":"We took all that down, and we found beautiful wooden floors,"},{"time":294000,"text":"whitewashed beams and it had the look --"},{"time":298000,"text":"while we were renovating this place, somebody said,"},{"time":300000,"text":"\"You know, it really kind of looks like the hull of a ship.\""},{"time":302000,"text":"And we looked around and somebody else said,"},{"time":306000,"text":"\"Well, you should sell supplies to the working buccaneer.\" (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":309000,"text":"And so this is what we did. So it made everybody laugh,"},{"time":314000,"text":"and we said, \"There's a point to that."},{"time":317000,"text":"Let's sell pirate supplies.\" This is the pirate supply store."},{"time":322000,"text":"You see, this is sort of a sketch I did on a napkin."},{"time":326000,"text":"A great carpenter built all this stuff and you see,"},{"time":329000,"text":"we made it look sort of pirate supply-like."},{"time":332000,"text":"Here you see planks sold by the foot"},{"time":335000,"text":"and we have supplies to combat scurvy."},{"time":338000,"text":"We have the peg legs there, that are all handmade and fitted to you."},{"time":343000,"text":"Up at the top, you see the eyepatch display,"},{"time":346000,"text":"which is the black column there for everyday use"},{"time":349000,"text":"for your eyepatch, and then you have the pastel"},{"time":353000,"text":"and other colors for stepping out at night --"},{"time":355000,"text":"special occasions, bar mitzvahs and whatever."}]},{"cues":[{"time":359000,"text":"So we opened this place. And this is a vat"},{"time":365000,"text":"that we fill with treasures that students dig in."},{"time":367000,"text":"This is replacement eyes in case you lose one."},{"time":371000,"text":"These are some signs that we have all over the place:"},{"time":374000,"text":"\"Practical Joking with Pirates.\""},{"time":377000,"text":"While you're reading the sign, we pull a rope behind the counter"},{"time":380000,"text":"and eight mop heads drop on your head."},{"time":384000,"text":"That was just my one thing -- I said we had to have something that drops on people's heads."},{"time":388000,"text":"It became mop heads. And this is the fish theater,"},{"time":393000,"text":"which is just a saltwater tank with three seats,"},{"time":396000,"text":"and then right behind it we set up this space,"},{"time":402000,"text":"which was the tutoring center."},{"time":404000,"text":"So right there is the tutoring center,"},{"time":406000,"text":"and then behind the curtain were the McSweeney's offices,"},{"time":408000,"text":"where all of us would be working on the magazine and book editing and things like that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":411000,"text":"The kids would come in --"},{"time":413000,"text":"or we thought they would come in. I should back up."},{"time":415000,"text":"We set the place up, we opened up, we spent months and months"},{"time":420000,"text":"renovating this place."},{"time":422000,"text":"We had tables, chairs, computers, everything."},{"time":425000,"text":"I went to a dot-com auction at a Holiday Inn in Palo Alto"},{"time":429000,"text":"and I bought 11 G4s with a stroke of a paddle."},{"time":434000,"text":"Anyway, we bought 'em, we set everything up and then we waited."},{"time":441000,"text":"It was started with about 12 of my friends,"},{"time":443000,"text":"people that I had known for years that were writers in the neighborhood."},{"time":446000,"text":"And we sat. And at 2:30 p.m. we put a sandwich board out on the front sidewalk"},{"time":450000,"text":"and it just said, \"Free Tutoring for Your English-Related"},{"time":453000,"text":"and Writing-Related Needs -- Just Come In, It's All Free.\""},{"time":456000,"text":"And we thought, \"Oh, they're going to storm the gates,"},{"time":459000,"text":"they're gonna love it.\" And they didn't."},{"time":462000,"text":"And so we waited, we sat at the tables, we waited and waited."},{"time":465000,"text":"And everybody was becoming very discouraged"},{"time":468000,"text":"because it was weeks and weeks that we waited, really, where nobody came in."}]},{"cues":[{"time":471000,"text":"And then somebody alerted us to the fact"},{"time":475000,"text":"that maybe there was a trust gap,"},{"time":477000,"text":"because we were operating behind a pirate supply store. (Laughter)"},{"time":486000,"text":"We never put it together, you know?"},{"time":489000,"text":"And so then, around that time, I persuaded a woman named Nineveh Caligari,"},{"time":497000,"text":"a longtime San Francisco educator --"},{"time":499000,"text":"she was teaching in Mexico City,"},{"time":501000,"text":"she had all the experience necessary,"},{"time":503000,"text":"knew everything about education,"},{"time":505000,"text":"was connected with all the teachers and community members in the neighborhood --"},{"time":507000,"text":"I convinced her to move up from Mexico City where she was teaching."},{"time":509000,"text":"She took over as executive director."},{"time":511000,"text":"Immediately, she made the inroads with the teachers"},{"time":514000,"text":"and the parents and the students and everything,"},{"time":517000,"text":"and so suddenly it was actually full every day."}]},{"cues":[{"time":519000,"text":"And what we were trying to offer every day"},{"time":521000,"text":"was one-on-one attention."},{"time":523000,"text":"The goal was to have a one-to-one ratio with every one of these students."},{"time":525000,"text":"You know, it's been proven"},{"time":527000,"text":"that 35 to 40 hours a year with one-on-one attention,"},{"time":530000,"text":"a student can get one grade level higher."},{"time":532000,"text":"And so most of these students, English is not spoken in the home."},{"time":535000,"text":"They come there, many times their parents --"},{"time":537000,"text":"you can't see it, but there's a church pew"},{"time":539000,"text":"that I bought in a Berkeley auction right there --"},{"time":541000,"text":"the parents will sometimes watch while their kids are being tutored."},{"time":544000,"text":"So that was the basis of it,"},{"time":546000,"text":"was one-on-one attention."},{"time":548000,"text":"And we found ourselves full every day with kids."},{"time":551000,"text":"If you're on Valencia Street within those few blocks at around 2 p.m.,"},{"time":555000,"text":"2:30 p.m., you will get run over, often,"},{"time":558000,"text":"by the kids and their big backpacks, or whatever, actually running to this space,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":561000,"text":"which is very strange, because it's school, in a way."},{"time":565000,"text":"But there was something psychological happening there"},{"time":569000,"text":"that was just a little bit different."},{"time":571000,"text":"And the other thing was, there was no stigma."},{"time":573000,"text":"Kids weren't going into the \"Center-for-Kids-That-Need-More-Help,\""},{"time":576000,"text":"or something like that. It was 826 Valencia."},{"time":579000,"text":"First of all, it was a pirate supply store, which is insane."},{"time":582000,"text":"And then secondly, there's a publishing company in the back."},{"time":586000,"text":"And so our interns were actually working"},{"time":588000,"text":"at the same tables very often,"},{"time":590000,"text":"and shoulder-to-shoulder, computer-next-to-computer with the students."}]},{"cues":[{"time":593000,"text":"And so it became a tutoring center --"},{"time":595000,"text":"publishing center, is what we called it --"},{"time":597000,"text":"and a writing center."},{"time":599000,"text":"They go in, and they might be working with a high school student"},{"time":601000,"text":"actually working on a novel -- because we had very gifted kids, too."},{"time":604000,"text":"So there's no stigma."},{"time":606000,"text":"They're all working next to each other. It's all a creative endeavor."},{"time":608000,"text":"They're seeing adults. They're modeling their behavior."},{"time":610000,"text":"These adults, they're working in their field."},{"time":613000,"text":"They can lean over, ask a question of one of these adults"},{"time":616000,"text":"and it all sort of feeds on each other."},{"time":619000,"text":"There's a lot of cross-pollination. The only problem,"},{"time":621000,"text":"especially for the adults working at McSweeney's"},{"time":624000,"text":"who hadn't necessarily bought into all of this when they signed up,"},{"time":627000,"text":"was that there was just the one bathroom. (Laughter)"},{"time":631000,"text":"With like 60 kids a day, this is a problem."}]},{"cues":[{"time":634000,"text":"But you know, there's something about the kids finishing their homework"},{"time":636000,"text":"in a given day, working one-on-one, getting all this attention --"},{"time":639000,"text":"they go home, they're finished. They don't stall."},{"time":642000,"text":"They don't do their homework in front of the TV."},{"time":644000,"text":"They're allowed to go home at 5:30 p.m., enjoy their family,"},{"time":647000,"text":"enjoy other hobbies, get outside, play."},{"time":650000,"text":"And that makes a happy family."},{"time":652000,"text":"A bunch of happy families in a neighborhood is a happy community."},{"time":655000,"text":"A bunch of happy communities tied together is a happy city and a happy world."},{"time":658000,"text":"So the key to it all is homework! (Laughter) (Applause)"},{"time":663000,"text":"There you have it, you know -- one-on-one attention."}]},{"cues":[{"time":667000,"text":"So we started off with about 12 volunteers,"},{"time":669000,"text":"and then we had about 50,"},{"time":671000,"text":"and then a couple hundred."},{"time":673000,"text":"And we now have 1,400 volunteers on our roster."},{"time":676000,"text":"And we make it incredibly easy to volunteer."},{"time":678000,"text":"The key thing is, even if you only have a couple of hours a month,"},{"time":681000,"text":"those two hours shoulder-to-shoulder,"},{"time":683000,"text":"next to one student, concentrated attention,"},{"time":685000,"text":"shining this beam of light on their work,"},{"time":688000,"text":"on their thoughts and their self-expression,"},{"time":691000,"text":"is going to be absolutely transformative,"},{"time":693000,"text":"because so many of the students have not had that ever before."},{"time":696000,"text":"So we said, \"Even if you have two hours one Sunday every six months,"},{"time":700000,"text":"it doesn't matter. That's going to be enough.\""},{"time":702000,"text":"So that's partly why the tutor corps grew so fast."}]},{"cues":[{"time":704000,"text":"Then we said, \"Well, what are we"},{"time":706000,"text":"going to do with the space during the day,"},{"time":708000,"text":"because it has to be used before 2:30 p.m.?\""},{"time":710000,"text":"So we started bringing in classes during the day."},{"time":712000,"text":"So every day, there's a field trip where they together create a book --"},{"time":715000,"text":"you can see it being typed up above."},{"time":717000,"text":"This is one of the classes getting way too excited about writing."},{"time":722000,"text":"You just point a camera at a class,"},{"time":724000,"text":"and it always looks like this."},{"time":726000,"text":"So this is one of the books that they do."},{"time":729000,"text":"Notice the title of the book,"},{"time":731000,"text":"\"The Book That Was Never Checked Out: Titanic.\""},{"time":735000,"text":"And the first line of that book is, \"Once there was a book named Cindy"},{"time":742000,"text":"that was about the Titanic.\""},{"time":745000,"text":"So, meanwhile, there's an adult in the back typing this up,"},{"time":748000,"text":"taking it completely seriously, which blows their mind."}]},{"cues":[{"time":751000,"text":"So then we still had more tutors to use."},{"time":754000,"text":"This is a shot of just some of the tutors during one of the events."},{"time":758000,"text":"The teachers that we work with --"},{"time":760000,"text":"and everything is different to teachers -- they tell us what to do."},{"time":763000,"text":"We went in there thinking,"},{"time":765000,"text":"\"We're ultimately, completely malleable. You're going to tell us."},{"time":766000,"text":"The neighborhood's going to tell us, the parents are going to tell us."},{"time":768000,"text":"The teachers are going to tell us how we're most useful.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":770000,"text":"So then they said, \"Why don't you come into the schools?"},{"time":773000,"text":"Because what about the students that wouldn't come to you,"},{"time":776000,"text":"necessarily, who don't have really active parents that are bringing them in,"},{"time":779000,"text":"or aren't close enough?\" So then we started saying,"},{"time":781000,"text":"\"Well, we've got 1,400 people on our tutor roster."},{"time":784000,"text":"Let's just put out the word.\" A teacher will say,"},{"time":786000,"text":"\"I need 12 tutors for the next five Sundays."},{"time":789000,"text":"We're working on our college essays. Send them in.\""},{"time":792000,"text":"So we put that out on the wire: 1,400 tutors."},{"time":794000,"text":"Whoever can make it signs up. They go in about a half an hour before the class."},{"time":797000,"text":"The teacher tells them what to do,"},{"time":799000,"text":"how to do it, what their training is, what their project is so far."},{"time":801000,"text":"They work under the teacher's guide,"},{"time":803000,"text":"and it's all in one big room."},{"time":805000,"text":"And that's actually the brunt of what we do is,"},{"time":807000,"text":"people going straight from their workplace, straight from home,"},{"time":809000,"text":"straight into the classroom and"},{"time":811000,"text":"working directly with the students."},{"time":813000,"text":"So then we're able to work with thousands and thousands of more students."},{"time":817000,"text":"Then another school said, \"Well, what if we"},{"time":819000,"text":"just give you a classroom and you can staff it all day?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":822000,"text":"So this is the Everett Middle School Writers' Room,"},{"time":825000,"text":"where we decorated it in buccaneer style."},{"time":827000,"text":"It's right off the library. And there we serve"},{"time":829000,"text":"all 529 kids in this middle school."},{"time":831000,"text":"This is their newspaper, the \"Straight-Up News,\""},{"time":834000,"text":"that has an ongoing column from Mayor Gavin Newsom"},{"time":837000,"text":"in both languages -- English and Spanish."},{"time":840000,"text":"So then one day Isabel Allende wrote to us and said,"},{"time":845000,"text":"\"Hey, why don't you assign a book with high school students?"},{"time":848000,"text":"I want them to write about how to achieve peace in a violent world.\""},{"time":852000,"text":"And so we went into Thurgood Marshall High School,"},{"time":854000,"text":"which is a school that we had worked with on some other things,"},{"time":857000,"text":"and we gave that assignment to the students."},{"time":860000,"text":"And we said, \"Isabel Allende is going to read all your essays at the end."},{"time":863000,"text":"She's going to publish them in a book."},{"time":865000,"text":"She's going to sponsor the printing of this book in paperback form."},{"time":867000,"text":"It's going to be available in all the bookstores in the Bay Area"},{"time":869000,"text":"and throughout the world, on Amazon and you name it.\""},{"time":872000,"text":"So these kids worked harder"},{"time":874000,"text":"than they've ever worked on anything in their lives,"},{"time":876000,"text":"because there was that outside audience,"},{"time":878000,"text":"there was Isabel Allende on the other end."},{"time":881000,"text":"I think we had about 170 tutors that worked on this book with them"},{"time":885000,"text":"and so this worked out incredibly well."},{"time":887000,"text":"We had a big party at the end."},{"time":889000,"text":"This is a book that you can find anywhere. So that led to a series of these."},{"time":892000,"text":"You can see Amy Tan sponsored the next one,"},{"time":894000,"text":"\"I Might Get Somewhere.\""},{"time":896000,"text":"And this became an ongoing thing. More and more books."}]},{"cues":[{"time":899000,"text":"Now we're sort of addicted to the book thing."},{"time":902000,"text":"The kids will work harder than they've ever worked in their life"},{"time":905000,"text":"if they know it's going to be permanent,"},{"time":907000,"text":"know it's going to be on a shelf,"},{"time":909000,"text":"know that nobody can diminish what they've thought and said,"},{"time":912000,"text":"that we've honored their words, honored their thoughts"},{"time":914000,"text":"with hundreds of hours of five drafts, six drafts --"},{"time":916000,"text":"all this attention that we give to their thoughts."},{"time":918000,"text":"And once they achieve that level, once they've written at that level,"},{"time":923000,"text":"they can never go back."},{"time":925000,"text":"It's absolutely transformative."},{"time":927000,"text":"And so then they're all sold in the store. This is near the planks."},{"time":929000,"text":"We sell all the student books."},{"time":931000,"text":"Where else would you put them, right?"},{"time":934000,"text":"So we sell 'em, and then something weird had been happening"},{"time":937000,"text":"with the stores. The store, actually --"},{"time":940000,"text":"even though we started out as just a gag -- the store actually made money."},{"time":945000,"text":"So it was paying the rent."},{"time":949000,"text":"And maybe this is just a San Francisco thing --"},{"time":951000,"text":"I don't know, I don't want to judge."},{"time":953000,"text":"But people would come in --"},{"time":955000,"text":"and this was before the pirate movies and everything!"},{"time":957000,"text":"It was making a lot of money. Not a lot of money,"},{"time":960000,"text":"but it was paying the rent, paying a full-time staff member there."},{"time":962000,"text":"There's the ocean maps you can see on the left."}]},{"cues":[{"time":964000,"text":"And it became a gateway to the community."},{"time":968000,"text":"People would come in and say, \"What the --?"},{"time":970000,"text":"What is this?\" I don't want to swear on the web. (Laughter)"},{"time":976000,"text":"Is that a rule? I don't know."},{"time":979000,"text":"They would say, \"What is this?\""},{"time":982000,"text":"And people would come in and learn more about it."},{"time":986000,"text":"And then right beyond -- there's usually a little chain there --"},{"time":989000,"text":"right beyond, they would see the kids being tutored."},{"time":991000,"text":"This is a field trip going on. And so they would be shopping,"},{"time":993000,"text":"and they might be more likely to buy some lard,"},{"time":995000,"text":"or millet for their parrot, or, you know, a hook,"},{"time":998000,"text":"or hook protector for nighttime, all of these things we sell."},{"time":1001000,"text":"So the store actually did really well."},{"time":1004000,"text":"But it brought in so many people --"},{"time":1006000,"text":"teachers, donors, volunteers, everybody --"},{"time":1007000,"text":"because it was street level. It was open to the public."},{"time":1009000,"text":"It wasn't a non-profit buried, you know, on the 30th floor"},{"time":1011000,"text":"of some building downtown. It was right in the neighborhood"},{"time":1014000,"text":"that it was serving, and it was open all the time to the public."},{"time":1017000,"text":"So, it became this sort of weird, happy accident."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1020000,"text":"So all the people I used to know in Brooklyn, they said,"},{"time":1022000,"text":"\"Well, why don't we have a place like that here?\""},{"time":1024000,"text":"And a lot of them had been former educators"},{"time":1026000,"text":"or would-be educators, so they combined"},{"time":1028000,"text":"with a lot of local designers, local writers,"},{"time":1030000,"text":"and they just took the idea independently"},{"time":1032000,"text":"and they did their own thing."},{"time":1034000,"text":"They didn't want to sell pirate supplies."},{"time":1036000,"text":"They didn't think that that was going to work there."},{"time":1039000,"text":"So, knowing the crime-fighting community in New York,"},{"time":1042000,"text":"they opened the Brooklyn Superhero Supply Company."},{"time":1045000,"text":"This is Sam Potts' great design that did this."},{"time":1048000,"text":"And this was to make it look sort of like one of those"},{"time":1050000,"text":"keysmith's shops that has to have every service"},{"time":1052000,"text":"they've ever offered, you know, all over there."},{"time":1055000,"text":"So they opened this place. Inside, it's like a Costco"},{"time":1057000,"text":"for superheroes -- all the supplies in kind of basic form."},{"time":1061000,"text":"These are all handmade."},{"time":1063000,"text":"These are all sort of repurposed other products, or whatever."},{"time":1066000,"text":"All the packaging is done by Sam Potts."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1068000,"text":"So then you have the villain containment unit,"},{"time":1071000,"text":"where kids put their parents. You have the office."},{"time":1073000,"text":"This is a little vault -- you have to put your product in there,"},{"time":1077000,"text":"it goes up an electric lift"},{"time":1079000,"text":"and then the guy behind the counter tells you"},{"time":1081000,"text":"that you have to recite the vow of heroism,"},{"time":1084000,"text":"which you do, if you want to buy anything. And it limits, really, their sales."},{"time":1088000,"text":"Personally, I think it's a problem."},{"time":1090000,"text":"Because they have to do it hand on heart and everything."},{"time":1092000,"text":"These are some of the products. These are all handmade."},{"time":1098000,"text":"This is a secret identity kit."},{"time":1100000,"text":"If you want to take on the identity of Sharon Boone,"},{"time":1102000,"text":"one American female marketing executive"},{"time":1104000,"text":"from Hoboken, New Jersey. It's a full dossier"},{"time":1106000,"text":"on everything you would need to know about Sharon Boone."},{"time":1108000,"text":"So, this is the capery where you get fitted for your cape,"},{"time":1113000,"text":"and then you walk up these three steel-graded steps"},{"time":1115000,"text":"and then we turn on three hydraulic fans"},{"time":1118000,"text":"from every side and then you can see the cape in action."},{"time":1121000,"text":"There's nothing worse than, you know,"},{"time":1123000,"text":"getting up there and the cape is bunching up or something like that."},{"time":1128000,"text":"So then, the secret door --"},{"time":1131000,"text":"this is one of the shelves you don't see"},{"time":1133000,"text":"when you walk in, but it slowly opens."},{"time":1135000,"text":"You can see it there in the middle next to all the grappling hooks."},{"time":1137000,"text":"It opens and then this is the tutoring center in the back. (Applause)"},{"time":1140000,"text":"So you can see the full effect!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1146000,"text":"But this is -- I just want to emphasize --"},{"time":1149000,"text":"locally funded, locally built."},{"time":1151000,"text":"All the designers, all of the builders,"},{"time":1153000,"text":"everybody was local, all the time was pro-bono."},{"time":1155000,"text":"I just came and visited and said, \"Yes, you guys are doing great,\""},{"time":1157000,"text":"or whatever. That was it. You can see the time"},{"time":1159000,"text":"in all five boroughs of New York in the back. (Laughter) (Applause)"},{"time":1165000,"text":"So this is the space during tutoring hours."},{"time":1168000,"text":"It's very busy. Same principles: one-on-one attention,"},{"time":1171000,"text":"complete devotion to the students' work"},{"time":1173000,"text":"and a boundless optimism and sort of a possibility"},{"time":1176000,"text":"of creativity and ideas."},{"time":1178000,"text":"And this switch is flicked in their heads"},{"time":1180000,"text":"when they walk through those 18 feet of this bizarre store, right?"},{"time":1183000,"text":"So it's school, but it's not school."},{"time":1185000,"text":"It's clearly not school, even though"},{"time":1187000,"text":"they're working shoulder-to-shoulder on tables, pencils and papers, whatever."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1189000,"text":"This is one of the students, Khaled Hamdan."},{"time":1191000,"text":"You can read this quote."},{"time":1193000,"text":"Addicted to video games and TV. Couldn't concentrate at home."},{"time":1195000,"text":"Came in. Got this concentrated attention."},{"time":1198000,"text":"And he couldn't escape it."},{"time":1200000,"text":"So, soon enough, he was writing. He would finish his homework early --"},{"time":1204000,"text":"got really addicted to finishing his homework early."},{"time":1206000,"text":"It's an addictive thing to sort of be done with it,"},{"time":1209000,"text":"and to have it checked, and to know he's going to achieve"},{"time":1211000,"text":"the next thing and be prepared for school the next day."},{"time":1213000,"text":"So he got hooked on that, and then he started doing other things."},{"time":1215000,"text":"He's now been published in five books."},{"time":1217000,"text":"He co-wrote a mockumentary about failed superheroes"},{"time":1219000,"text":"called \"Super-Has-Beens.\""},{"time":1223000,"text":"He wrote a series on \"Penguin Balboa,\""},{"time":1226000,"text":"which is a fighting -- a boxing -- penguin."},{"time":1229000,"text":"And then he read aloud just a few weeks ago to 500 people at Symphony Space,"},{"time":1234000,"text":"at a benefit for 826 New York. So he's there every day."},{"time":1237000,"text":"He's evangelical about it. He brings his cousins in now."},{"time":1240000,"text":"There's four family members that come in every day."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1243000,"text":"So, I'll go through really quickly."},{"time":1245000,"text":"This is L.A., The Echo Park Time Travel Mart:"},{"time":1248000,"text":"\"Whenever You Are, We're Already Then.\" (Laughter)"},{"time":1253000,"text":"This is sort of a 7-Eleven for time travelers."},{"time":1256000,"text":"So you see everything: it's exactly as a 7-Eleven would be."},{"time":1259000,"text":"Leeches. Mammoth chunks. They even have their own Slurpee machine:"},{"time":1264000,"text":"\"Out of Order. Come Back Yesterday.\" (Laughter) (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1274000,"text":"Anyway. So I'm going to jump ahead."},{"time":1277000,"text":"These are spaces that are only affiliated with us,"},{"time":1280000,"text":"doing this same thing: Word St. in Pittsfield, Massachusetts;"},{"time":1283000,"text":"Ink Spot in Cincinnati; Youth Speaks, San Francisco, California,"},{"time":1285000,"text":"which inspired us; Studio St. Louis in St. Louis;"},{"time":1288000,"text":"Austin Bat Cave in Austin;"},{"time":1291000,"text":"Fighting Words in Dublin, Ireland, started by Roddy Doyle,"},{"time":1294000,"text":"this will be open in April."},{"time":1296000,"text":"Now I'm going to the TED Wish -- is that okay?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1300000,"text":"All right, I've got a minute. So, the TED Wish:"},{"time":1303000,"text":"I wish that you -- you personally and every creative individual"},{"time":1306000,"text":"and organization you know -- will find a way"},{"time":1308000,"text":"to directly engage with a public school in your area"},{"time":1311000,"text":"and that you'll then tell the story of how you got involved,"},{"time":1314000,"text":"so that within a year we have a thousand examples --"},{"time":1316000,"text":"a thousand! -- of transformative partnerships."},{"time":1318000,"text":"Profound leaps forward!"},{"time":1320000,"text":"And these can be things that maybe you're already doing."},{"time":1322000,"text":"I know that so many people in this room"},{"time":1324000,"text":"are already doing really interesting things."},{"time":1326000,"text":"I know that for a fact. So, tell us these stories and inspire others on the website."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1330000,"text":"We created a website."},{"time":1332000,"text":"I'm going to switch to \"we,\" and not \"I,\" hope:"},{"time":1335000,"text":"We hope that the attendees of this conference will usher in"},{"time":1338000,"text":"a new era of participation in our public schools."},{"time":1340000,"text":"We hope that you will take the lead"},{"time":1342000,"text":"in partnering your innovative spirit and expertise"},{"time":1344000,"text":"with that of innovative educators in your community."},{"time":1347000,"text":"Always let the teachers lead the way."},{"time":1349000,"text":"They will tell you how to be useful. I hope that you'll step in and help out."},{"time":1353000,"text":"There are a million ways."},{"time":1355000,"text":"You can walk up to your local school"},{"time":1356000,"text":"and consult with the teachers. They'll always tell you how to help."},{"time":1359000,"text":"So, this is with Hot Studio in San Francisco,"},{"time":1362000,"text":"they did this phenomenal job."},{"time":1363000,"text":"This website is already up, it's already got a bunch of stories,"},{"time":1366000,"text":"a lot of ideas. It's called \"Once Upon a School,\""},{"time":1369000,"text":"which is a great title, I think."},{"time":1370000,"text":"This site will document every story, every project that comes"},{"time":1372000,"text":"out of this conference and around the world. So you go to the website,"},{"time":1376000,"text":"you see a bunch of ideas you can be inspired by"},{"time":1378000,"text":"and then you add your own projects once you get started."},{"time":1381000,"text":"Hot Studio did a great job in a very tight deadline. So, visit the site."},{"time":1385000,"text":"If you have any questions, you can ask this guy,"},{"time":1388000,"text":"who's our director of national programs. He'll be on the phone."},{"time":1391000,"text":"You email him, he'll answer any question you possibly want."},{"time":1393000,"text":"And he'll get you inspired and get you going"},{"time":1396000,"text":"and guide you through the process so that you can affect change."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1399000,"text":"And it can be fun! That's the point of this talk --"},{"time":1401000,"text":"it needn't be sterile. It needn't be bureaucratically untenable."},{"time":1408000,"text":"You can do and use the skills that you have."},{"time":1412000,"text":"The schools need you. The teachers need you."},{"time":1414000,"text":"Students and parents need you. They need your actual person:"},{"time":1417000,"text":"your physical personhood and your open minds"},{"time":1419000,"text":"and open ears and boundless compassion,"},{"time":1422000,"text":"sitting next to them, listening and nodding"},{"time":1424000,"text":"and asking questions for hours at a time."},{"time":1427000,"text":"Some of these kids just don't plain know how good they are:"},{"time":1431000,"text":"how smart and how much they have to say."},{"time":1434000,"text":"You can tell them. You can shine that light on them,"},{"time":1437000,"text":"one human interaction at a time. So we hope you'll join us."},{"time":1441000,"text":"Thank you so much."}]}]}